{
  "stem": "1249.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said to us, don't you recognize me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was our grandfather.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took his-- he had to take his beard off, had to take the payots off.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he only-- I think he had a hat on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he looked different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was so much optimism.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She said-- he said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nothing will happen to you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then he said, I want to pray for you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[SOBS] And he put-- [SOBS] few minute, please.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 13 SECONDS] He put his hand on my head.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he prayed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bentshn, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know bentshn?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He benched me, and same with, with my mother-- with my sister.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother was not there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I always said, if my mother would be there, probably she still be alive, but-- because I believe God, God listened to my grandfather prayer.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he prayed for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Same, same day, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Every Friday night, he benched us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where was your mother at that time?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I can't-- I, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were just get up from there for this place was so small place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe just we were going a little bit, looking around to maybe look for-- maybe look for, I'm sure for our grandfather.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was in a different place, and was ready to take everybody to-- out to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know where we are going to go, who is going to take us, what's going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he found us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he benched us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I feel God helped to-- I think-- I think-- I know he was listening to his prayer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think just a few days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's my feeling.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
